    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>When you take this oath at 3rd level, you gain the following two Channel Divinity options.</p><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Champion Challenge\" data-source=\"SCAG\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\" title=\"Source: Sword Coast Adventurer’s Guide, p132\">Champion Challenge</span></h3> <p>As a bonus action, you issue a challenge that compels other creatures to do battle with you. Each creature of your choice that you can see within 30 feet of you must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, a creature can't willingly move more than 30 feet away from you. This effect ends on the creature if you are &amp;Reference[condition=incapacitated] or die or if the creature is more than 30 feet away from you.</p></div><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Turn the Tide\" data-source=\"SCAG\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"2\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\" title=\"Source: Sword Coast Adventurer’s Guide, p132\">Turn the Tide</span></h3> <p>As a bonus action, you can bolster injured creatures with your Channel Divinity. Each creature of your choice that can hear you within 30 feet of you regains hit points equal to [[/r 1d6]] + your Charisma modifier (minimum of 1) if it has no more than half of its hit points.</p></div></div>",
